5   package net.sourceforge.pmd.typeresolution.testdata;
6   
7   import net.sourceforge.pmd.typeresolution.testdata.dummytypes.GenericClass;
8   
9   public class FieldAccessGenericParameter<T extends GenericClass<String, GenericClass<String, Integer>>,
10          S extends Double> {
11      T parameterGeneric;
12      S classGeneric;
13  
14      <M extends Character> void foo() {
15          M localGeneric = null;
16  
17          // access type dependant on class/method type arguments
18          // Primary[Prefix[Name[classGeneric]]]
19          classGeneric = null; // Double
20          localGeneric = null; // Character
21  
22  
23          // test type parameters extending generic types
24          // Primary[Prefix[Name[parameterGeneric.first]]]
25          parameterGeneric.second.second = new Integer(0);
26      }
27  
28      <C extends Number> FieldAccessGenericParameter() {
29          C constructorGeneric = null;
30  
31          // access type dependant on constructor type arugments
32          // Primary[Prefix[Name[localGeneric]]]
33          constructorGeneric = null; // Number
34      }
35  }
